Prism32 is a self-extending, self-repairing, self-evolving polymorphic AI
super-agent. One Python file, stdlib-only. Cross-platform terminal harness
with multi-model subagents, plugin self-generation, and autonomous goal
execution.

There is no fixed feature ceiling; every task expands what the agent can do.
It runs on modern PCs and older machines alike: no Node.js, no browser
runtime, no pip dependencies, and no local database server.
